---
import Button from '../components/button.astro';
import Projects from '../components/home/projects.astro';
import Separator from '../components/home/separator.astro';
import Writings from '../components/home/writings.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<Layout title="DerekBeau">
  <div class="relative z-20 mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-4xl px-7 md:mt-24 lg:mt-32 xl:px-0">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row">
      <div class="relative w-full md:w-1/2">
        <h1 class="mb-5 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight dark:text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl">
          Hi, I'm Derek.
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-6 text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          I specialize in combining marketing and code to create and scale profitable campaigns.
          With over two decades of experience running paid traffic and three decades of programming,
          I've spent my career solving interesting problems at the intersection of technology and
          business. These days, I'm based in Austin, TX, where I'm building projects, exploring new
          ideas, and raising a family.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-2 font-semibold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
          Here's what I'm working on now:
        </p>
        <ul
          class="space-y-[3px] py-2 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 [&>li]:relative [&>li]:pl-4
            before:[&>li]:absolute before:[&>li]:left-0 before:[&>li]:content-['•']"
        >
          <li>Building web and mobile apps with React and React Native</li>
          <li>Staying sharp on marketing technology and experimenting with automation</li>
          <li>Exploring the potential of AI tools in marketing, software, and more</li>
          <li>
            Writing and sharing insights about indie hacking, solopreneurship, and personal growth
          </li>
          <li>Diving deeper into blockchain, crypto, and web3 development</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="my-6 text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          This site is a space for me to share my projects, interests, and ideas—a mix of blog and
          portfolio. It's where I document what I'm working on, connect with like-minded people, and
          hold myself accountable to keep shipping.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6 text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          If any of this resonates, feel free to <a
            href="http://x.com/derekbeau"
            class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700">follow me on X</a
          > or connect with me on <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/derekbeau/"
            class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700">LinkedIn</a
          >. If any of this resonates, feel free to follow me on X or connect with me on LinkedIn.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          Send me a DM if you’re working on something exciting in marketing, code, or creative
          problem-solving—I’m always open to collaborating, sharing ideas, or helping solve
          challenging problems.
        </p>
        <Button text="Follow me on 𝕏" link="https://x.com/derekbeau" />
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative mt-10 hidden w-full justify-end md:flex md:w-1/2 md:translate-y-4 md:pl-10 xl:translate-y-0"
      >
        <div class="relative w-full">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/photo-derek.jpeg"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="auto"
            class="relative mx-auto h-64 w-64 rounded-full border-4 border-white object-cover shadow-lg
              dark:border-neutral-800"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- <Separator text="Check out my projects" />
  <Projects />
  <Separator text="Some of my writing" />
  <Writings /> -->
</Layout>
